cff-version: 1.2.0
title: "ExactK: Iso-K Hinge Loss for K-Leakage-Free QEC Decoding"
message: "If you use this software, please cite it as below."
type: software
version: 1.0.0
date-released: "2026-03-03"
license: MIT
